---
import SocialList from "@/components/SocialList.astro";
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<PageLayout meta={{ title: "Home" }}>
	<section>
		<h1 class="title mb-3">Hi, I’m Hamza.</h1>

		<div class="mb-8">
			<SocialList/>
		</div>

		<p class="mb-5 text-base sm:text-lg">
			I’m a research-oriented AI engineer specialising in multimodal generative AI systems and retrieval-augmented generation.
			I graduated from Heriot-Watt University in 2025 with a First-Class Honours BSc in Computer Science with a specialisation in AI.
			My core focus and aspirations are researching, developing, and deploying reliable and safety-critical AI across various domain and mediums.
		</p>

		<div class="space-y-6">
			<div>
				<h2 class="title mb-2 text-lg">Now</h2>
				<p class="mb-0">
					Benchmarking vision-language models under domain shift (lab ↔ field) for crop disease classification, and
					building evaluation-driven RAG agents for medical QA.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div>
				<h2 class="title mb-2 text-lg">Previously</h2>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
					<li>Led a RAG-enabled medical QA agent (FAISS + Llama) and measured quality with/without retrieval.</li>
					<li>Built a “Learning Buddy” RAG pipeline (LlamaIndex + Milvus) and deployed a Streamlit demo via Docker.</li>
					<li>Trained and evaluated CNN baselines (ResNet-50) and VLM variants (zero-shot, probing, LoRA).</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div>
				<h2 class="title mb-2 text-lg">Interests</h2>
				<p class="mb-0">
					Agentic multimodal systems, grounded reasoning, and practical safety constraints — turning “works on my dataset”
					into “works when it matters.”
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
			<a class="btn" href="/projects/">Projects</a>
			<a class="btn" href="/publications/">Publications</a>
			<a class="btn" href="/cv/">Download CV</a>
			<a class="btn" href="/contact/">Contact</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>